channel.title: Need some information help
channel.description:
I don't want to just be told how to do this but if someone can give me a link to a guide that would help me out. Im trying to find pi base customs. I look all over good and they only give this customs I don't want. I just want to learn how to make my own custom and add it my self. Or find a big group of customs and add them. Any idea where I can find this.
I did search google and they only give the scripts not good items and dont tell you where you need to add them or how to add them.
